 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, this is a short message from the Geneva office. Welcome again to the international team. At Sucafina, we work with coffee suppliers around the world. Your role is important. You handle contracts with our global clients, and you work with the export team every day. We are a remote team, so we talk by email and video calls. Have a great first week, and welcome aboard.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, this is Fernanda. I work at Sucafina, a global coffee company. My role is in the trading office. I work with international suppliers, and I help with export contracts. My team is remote, so we work from many countries. We do not work in the same office, but we talk every day. I love my new role, and I am ready to learn more.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_listening2.mp3"
 },
